1. Initial Configuration
    > git config --global user.name "Jack Hu"
    > git config --global user.email "..."
    > git config --global init.defaultBranch main

2. Four Important Blocks
    1. Working Directory
    2. Staging Area
    3. Local Repository
    4. Remote Repository

3. Common Used Commands
    > git init
    > git status

    > git add <file>
    > git commit -m "text"
    
    > git log
    > git diff

    > git branch <name>
        > git branch -c <name> # -c for create
    > git checkout <name>
    > git merge <name>

    > git remote add origin <URL>
    > git push -u origin main
    > git pull
    > git clone <URL>

4. Useful Packages
    1. tig
    2. lazygit
